trans-unit.source: Specifies whether a <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.Frame"></xref> uses its own journal.
trans-unit.target: 지정 여부는 <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.Frame"> </xref> 자체 저널을 사용 합니다.

trans-unit.source: JournalOwnership is used by the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.JournalOwnership*> property.

When JournalOwnership is Automatic, the following behavior applies: - The hosted <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame> behaves as though UsesParentJournal was set if it is hosted by either a <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame> or a <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>.
trans-unit.target: 자동 JournalOwnership을 사용 하는 경우 다음 동작이 적용 됩니다.-호스트 <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame>중 하나는 <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame>나 <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame> 의해 호스트 될 경우 UsesParentJournal 설정 된 것 처럼 동작</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame>

trans-unit.source: - The hosted <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame> behaves as though OwnsJournal was set if: - It is not directly hosted by either a <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame> or <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>.
trans-unit.target: -호스팅된 <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame>OwnsJournal 경우 설정 된 것 처럼 동작:-중 하나는 <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame>나 <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame> 에서 직접 호스트 되지 않는</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame>

trans-unit.source: - It is hosted by at least one <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame>, where each containing <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame> has its <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.JournalOwnership%2A> property is set to UsesParentJournal.
trans-unit.target: -호스팅되는지 하나 이상에서 <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame>여기서 각각 포함 된 <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame>가 해당 <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.JournalOwnership%2A>UsesParentJournal 속성이.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.JournalOwnership%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > once a <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame> creates its own journal, switching to Automatic has no effect.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > 되 면 한 <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame>자체 저널을 만들고 자동으로 전환 해도 효과가 없습니다.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame>

trans-unit.source: Whether or not this <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.Frame"></xref> will create and use its own journal depends on its parent.
trans-unit.target: 여부이 <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.Frame"> </xref> 만들고 사용 하 여 자체 저널 부모에 따라 달라 집니다.
<xref href="System.Windows.Controls.Frame"> </xref> 자체 저널을 유지 관리 합니다.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.Frame"></xref> uses the journal of the next available navigation host up the content tree, if available.
trans-unit.target: <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.Frame"> </xref> 사용 가능한 경우 다음 사용 가능한 탐색 호스트 콘텐츠 트리에서 저널을 사용 합니다.

trans-unit.source: Otherwise, navigation history is not maintained for the <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.Frame"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: 그렇지 않은 경우 탐색 기록에 대 한 유지 되지 않습니다는 <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.Frame"> </xref>합니다.
